Wmns Stan Smith 'Doodle'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Doodle’ carries a synthetic leather upper that incorporates Primegreen, made from high-performance recycled materials that constitute 50% of the sneaker’s build. The pristine white finish is enlivened by a series of colorful graphics bunched around the heel, each rendered in a hand-drawn, DIY look. They’re joined by traditional branding elements that include perforated three-stripes and a stamped Stan Smith tongue label in a subtle peach hue.

Jordan 9 Retro Change The World (W)
results.story: The women’s Air Jordan 9 Retro ‘Change the World’ marks the debut of the AJ9 in a women’s-exclusive colorway. The mid-top carries a white leather upper with contrasting black heel loops inscribed with the tagline ‘Change the World.’ Vegetable-tanned leather overlays, along with the sneaker’s molded eyelets, collar lining and midsole, are all finished in mismatched hues developed from natural plant-based dyes. Underfoot, the rubber outsole is etched with multilingual designs in a nod to MJ’s emergence as a global icon.

Nike Dunk Low College Navy Grey (W)
results.story: The women's Nike Dunk Low SP ‘College Navy’ delivers a two-tone colorway of the retro hoops shoe originally released in 1985. The all-leather upper combines a navy blue base with contrasting overlays in Wolf Grey. An unexpected pop of color arrives via Nike branding in University Red on the heel tab and woven tongue tag, while satin laces and a matching collar lining add to the shoe’s luxe look. A translucent rubber outsole offers grippy traction underfoot.

Samarria Brevard x Wmns Numeric 213 'White Blue'
results.story: Designed in collaboration with the Numeric team rider, the Samarria Brevard x New Balance women’s Numeric 213 ‘White Blue’ makes use of a canvas upper with a reinforced suede toe cap and ollie panel. The pristine white finish is contrasted by aqua-colored detailing on the heel tab and woven tongue tag. The former is embellished with a unique dragonfly graphic, the latter with dual NB and Samarria branding. A polyurethane insole provides lightweight cushioning, while a gum rubber outsole delivers grippy traction underfoot.

Nike Air Max 97 Swarovski Polar Blue (W)
results.story: The Swarovski x Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Polar Blue’ offers a luxe take on an OG colorway of the retro runner. The sneaker makes use of a silver mesh upper with fused overlays encrusted with tiny Swarovski crystals, adding shimmer to the sneaker’s water ripple-inspired lines. A pale blue mini-Swoosh adorns the lateral quarter panel and oval tongue patch. Buoyant cushioning arrives via a polyurethane midsole, fitted with a historic full-length Max Air unit.

results.name: Wmns Offcourt Duo Slide 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Offcourt Duo Slide ‘Black White’ delivers a premium take on the classic slide. The upper is composed of two black synthetic leather straps, both lined in 100% recycled fabric and the wider of the two stamped with a contrasting white Nike wordmark. A micro-texture on the Revive foam footbed is designed for non-slip comfort. A lightweight EVA outsole features a circular traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Skycourt 'Cream Lichen Rock'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Skycourt ‘Cream Lichen Rock’ features a subtle color palette inspired by springtime in Japan, executed on a retro build that takes its cues from the Gel Altitude volleyball shoe from 1990. The sneaker makes use of an ivory-colored twill upper with ASICS’ signature tiger stripes embroidered on the lateral quarter panel. A textured heel overlay in a pale green finish delivers a subtle pop of contrasting color. Anchoring the low-top is a rubber cupsole borrowed from the Japan S silhouette.

results.name: Wmns RS-Fast 'Safari'
results.story: The PUMA women’s RS-Fast ‘Safari’ dresses up the retro-inspired silhouette with varying shades of pink throughout a layered upper built with mesh, leather and no-sew synthetic skins. The pastel hues are joined by stylized animal prints on the breathable mesh tongue and molded TPU heel counter. PUMA’s signature Formstrip is relegated to a sculpted midsole built with cushy RS foam. A coral-tinged rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Blazer Low '77 'Triple White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Blazer Low ‘77 ‘Triple White’ treats the vintage hoops shoe to a pristine blank-slate finish. The upper is constructed from crisp white leather and branded with a matching white retro Swoosh, along with an embossed Nike wordmark on the heel tab. The tonal theme continues on a woven tag atop a vintage exposed-foam tongue. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic herringbone traction pattern originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: Wmns Lavante Terrain 'Black Ceramic Pink'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Lavante Terrain ‘Black Ceramic Pink’ highlights a simple two-tone finish on a versatile running shoe built to handle off-road use. Breathable black mesh on the upper is fortified with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with contrasting pink side stripes. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length FuelFoam midsole, supported by a high-traction rubber outsole that offers reliable grip through all conditions.

results.name: Wmns Air Max Bella TR 4 'White Green Glow'
Wmns Adilette Comfort Slide 'Legacy Purple'
results.story: The adidas women’s Adilette Comfort Slide ‘Legacy Purple’ updates the cushy sandal with an injected EVA midsole in a subtle violet hue. Step-in comfort is provided by the combination of a contoured footbed and a wide single-bandage upper, lined in quick-drying textile and marked with a repeating adidas logo. Underfoot, a durable synthetic outsole features a crisp white finish and a diamond traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Nike Air Max 97 Leopard (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Leopard’ features a unique design that blends twin inspirations drawn from the natural world. In addition to the sneaker’s wavy overlays, treated to a reflective finish and designed to mimic a water ripple effect, the textile and suede upper is covered in an all-over graphic made up of numerous leopard spots. Mini Swooshes in Peach Cream offer contrasting pops of color. The sneaker is mounted on a polyurethane midsole with full-length Max Air cushioning.

results.name: Wmns Superstar Boot 'Night Indigo'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar Boot ‘Night Indigo’ reimagines the vintage hoops shoe as a rugged outdoor boot. The monochromatic navy upper is constructed from lightweight nylon with tonal suede paneling at the heel and toe, the latter embellished with stitched lines that replicate the iconic shell toe of the original. The sneaker-boot hybrid is mounted on a black rubber sole unit, featuring a herringbone traction pattern for maximum grip.

results.name: Wmns Flex Experience Run 10 'Venice Crimson Bliss'
results.story: Designed for the casual runner, the Nike women’s Flex Experience Run 10 ‘Venice Crimson Bliss’ highlights delicate hues on a breathable mesh upper with supportive no-sew overlays and textile quarter panels marked with embroidered Swoosh branding. The lightweight build is placed atop a Nike Flex sole unit, featuring a series of cuts underfoot that promote the natural motion of the foot, ultimately yielding a smooth and comfortable ride.

results.name: Wmns Revolution 5 FlyEase 'Summit White Crimson Bliss'
results.story: The Nike women’s Revolution 5 FlyEase ‘Summit White Crimson Bliss’ bundles stretchy comfort and buoyant cushioning in a pastel-hued package. The pale green knit upper is secured with no-tie elastic laces and an adjustable hook-loop-strap, while zippered closure wraps around the back of the collar and allows the shoe to be easily slipped on and off. The sneaker rides on a full-length foam midsole with textured sidewalls designed to reduce overall weight. Reliable traction is provided by a rubber outsole, spaced to allow the foot to flex naturally.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Skychaser GTX 2.0 'Black Gum'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Skychaser GTX 2.0 ‘Black Gum’ delivers a neutral colorway of a rugged hiking shoe built with sustainability in mind. Recycled materials are incorporated into a breathable textile upper lined with a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with a stabilization frame and supported by a lugged Continental rubber outsole that offers reliable grip in all conditions.

results.name: Wmns Eris Reptile 'Marshmallow Pale Khaki'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Eris Reptile 'Marshmallow Pale Khaki’ shows off bold details on an otherwise restrained design, featuring a subdued shade of tan throughout the leather upper. A croc-embossed forefoot overlay gives way to a high-traction toe wrap built with gum rubber, while PUMA’s jumping cat logo shines in metallic gold on the black leather heel tab. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a PU-molded sockliner and a compression-molded EVA midsole.

results.name: Wmns Solar Boost 3 'Hi-Res Yellow'
results.story: The adidas women’s Solar Boost 3 ‘Hi-Res Yellow’ dresses the performance runner with a neon-colored engineered mesh upper, overlaid with seamless no-sew skins and reflective silver three-stripes. The seamless build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with a molded Contrail Rail for improved stability. In lieu of adidas’ standard Torsion bar, the shoe makes use of adidas’ Linear Energy Push system, which reduces forefoot flex for enhanced energy return.

results.name: Wmns Adilette Comfort Slide 'Clear Pink Leopard'
results.story: The adidas women’s Adilette Comfort Slide ‘Clear Pink Leopard’ combines elevated comfort with an eye-catching animal print. The upper takes the form of a wide synthetic-leather bandage strap, lined in soft textile and entirely covered in leopard spots. They’re joined by signature three-stripe branding in a pastel pink hue. A contrasting dark grey finish is applied to a lightweight Cloudfoam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a durable EVA outsole.

results.name: Wmns Eris Reptile 'White Pale Khaki'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Eris Reptile ‘White Pale Khaki’ pairs street-ready style with a versatile low-top silhouette. The minimalist white leather upper is reinforced with a suede forefoot overlay covered in a debossed croc print. A contrasting pop of color lands on a red leather heel tab, stamped with PUMA’s jumping cat logo in metallic gold. Lightweight cushioning is provided by the combination of a molded PU sockliner and a CMEVA midsole, featuring a rubber-wrapped forefoot for enhanced durability.

results.name: Wmns Solar Boost 3 'Black Screaming Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s Solar Boost 3 ‘Black Screaming Pink’ features highlighter accents on a performance running shoe that delivers a responsive and stable ride. The upper is constructed from black engineered mesh with seamless fuchsia overlays and silver reflective three-stripes. A full-length Boost midsole is reinforced with a molded Control Rail and a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole. Increased energy return is provided by adidas’ Linear Energy Push system.

results.name: Wmns LVL-UP XT 'Fiery Coral'
results.story: The PUMA women’s LVL-UP XT ‘Fiery Coral’ updates the lightweight training shoe with a breathable textile knit upper in a fluorescent finish. The lacing system is integrated into a supportive midfoot cage, accented with a contrasting white PUMA Formstrip on the lateral side. A molded TPU heel clip provides rearfoot stability. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a PROFOAM midsole, built with high-rebound EVA and enhanced with visible LQDCELL technology in the heel.

results.name: Wmns Supernova+ 'White Silver Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s Supernova+ ‘White Silver Pink’ offers seamless comfort via a one-piece mesh upper that wraps around the foot in breathable support. The sock-like build is energized by various candy-colored accents and shiny metallic silver overlays. They’re joined by reflective three-stripes in a matte grey finish. The running shoe’s hybrid tooling combines a full-length Bounce midsole with responsive Boost cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Wmns Supernova+ 'Grey Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas women’s Supernova+ ‘Grey Solar Yellow’ offers a blend of soft and responsive cushioning, bundled in a neutral-colored package with hi-vis accents. They include reflective silver three-stripes and seamless neon overlays, which enliven an engineered mesh upper composed of 100% recycled polyester. The streamlined build rests on a cushy Bounce midsole, enhanced with visible Boost inserts nestled in the heel and forefoot.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Adilette Slide 'Floral - White'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Adilette Slide ‘Floral’ dresses the versatile sandal in an ornate design, courtesy of the female-led print studio based in East London. A lush multicolor floral print decorates the wide bandage-strap upper, made with synthetic leather and accented with raised three-stripe branding. Dual adidas and Her Studio London branding is printed on a soft, contoured footbed that yields step-in comfort.
